snippet.title: Eyes of Hellfire - first announce
snippet.description:
Eyes of Hellfire
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1724030/Eyes_of_Hellfire/

A new game from Gambrinous

- Set in Ireland
- In the infamous HELLFIRE CLUB
- That is deliciously Gothic Horror
- Made by an Irish Studio
- And absolutely Co-Op

Wishlist today! https://store.steampowered.com/app/1724030/Eyes_of_Hellfire/
